Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.84,0:01:46.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pozri, Poe.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.08,0:01:47.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nie je to krásne?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.68,0:01:50.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dokážem to bez zápaliek.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.22,0:01:51.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Vidíš? Pozri.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.50,0:02:12.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.61,0:02:15.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pozri, mama. Nie je to krásne?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.91,0:02:20.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mama?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.52,0:02:24.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Diabol...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.99,0:02:29.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Epizóda 19\NInferno
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.07,0:02:42.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.10,0:02:43.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pán Aoki...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.64,0:02:50.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prepáčte.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.91,0:02:52.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Áno?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.21,0:02:53.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Um, chcel by som podať toto...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.05,0:02:55.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Takže rozvodové papiere.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.88,0:02:59.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Vyplníte to sám?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.45,0:03:00.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.06,0:03:05.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Um, nuž...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.59,0:03:07.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Vážne to môžem takto prijať?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.99,0:03:13.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chcem povedať, vyzeráte pri tom dosť váhavo...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.53,0:03:16.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ak o tom ešte debatujete, vrátim vám to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.77,0:03:21.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Je milé, že sa toľko obávate.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.37,0:03:23.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale je to v poriadku.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.24,0:03:25.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Už som sa rozhodol.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Takže ste ďalší...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.15,0:03:34.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Zapojený do konca sveta...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.79,0:03:36.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chápem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.12,0:03:37.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.42,0:03:40.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Čo dnes večer, ak by to nevadilo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.66,0:03:41.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dnes večer?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.96,0:03:43.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.30,0:03:45.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Večer o jedenástej na Tokijskej stanici.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.77,0:03:48.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rozumiem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.30,0:03:50.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,V tom prípade to prijmem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.67,0:03:51.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ďakujem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.38,0:04:00.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pán Aoki...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.70,0:04:20.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.27,0:04:24.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui Drakov zeme mi povedal...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.10,0:04:27.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Že dokážeš prísť na to, kto skutočne som.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.24,0:04:32.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aký význam má zistiť to?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.71,0:04:34.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Neviem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.51,0:04:35.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.72,0:04:41.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, Aoki.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.72,0:04:46.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Niekto menom slečna Kasumi z "Floweru" ťa volal.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.29,0:04:47.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Vraj jej máš zavolať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.76,0:04:50.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Flower"? Myslíš ten...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.66,0:04:51.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Á-Áno...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.06,0:04:53.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To vážne, Aoki?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.97,0:04:57.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,N-Nie, tak to nie je.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.34,0:05:02.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, poslať takého vážneho človeka ako Aoki na také miesto
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.31,0:05:03.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,bol vážne zlý nápad!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.84,0:05:07.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hovorí sa, že slušní ľudia do toho skôr spadnú.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.71,0:05:09.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-Tak to nie je!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.38,0:05:11.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bol som tam pracovne!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.38,0:05:12.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pracovne!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.42,0:05:16.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ak si dobre spomínam, vrátil si sa odtiaľ celkom šťastný.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.59,0:05:18.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hej, to je pravda.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.86,0:05:20.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,N-Nemožné.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.49,0:05:22.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-To je...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.23,0:05:24.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To pretože... Možno...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.16,0:05:27.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,FLOWER - Estetický štýl
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Toto ste potrebovali?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.30,0:05:30.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.54,0:05:33.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Je to cenná informácia, ktorú môže dať
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.61,0:05:35.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,len človek z tohto priemyslu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.34,0:05:37.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Moji autori budú veľmi šťastní.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.81,0:05:41.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pracovať vo vydavateľstve musí byť drina.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.28,0:05:43.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Keď idete až sem kvôli informáciám.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.75,0:05:45.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Spisovatelia sú veľmi zaneprázdnení ľudia,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.88,0:05:49.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,takže mojou prácou editora je pomôcť, ako môžem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.02,0:05:52.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chápem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.12,0:05:55.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mimochodom, máte rodinu?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.23,0:05:56.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mám ženu a dcéru.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.06,0:05:58.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To som si myslela.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.63,0:06:02.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Všetci dobrí muži sú ženatí.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.40,0:06:04.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, už je toľko hodín?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.14,0:06:09.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Určite ste sa chceli so mnou len porozprávať?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.74,0:06:11.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nuž, um, ja...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.68,0:06:14.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Myslíte, že vám doprajem len rozhovor?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.61,0:06:17.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Robím si srandu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.22,0:06:20.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Silno myslíte na vašu ženu a dcéru, však?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.85,0:06:24.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hej, sú pre mňa rodinou, ktorú chcem nadovšetko chrániť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.69,0:06:27.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Závidím vám takú rodinu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.03,0:06:30.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To je niečo, čo som nikdy nemala...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.80,0:06:34.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, prepáčte, že som vás zarmútila.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.40,0:06:36.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-To nič...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.27,0:06:38.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dnešok bol zábavný.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.30,0:06:41.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nabudúce príďte ako zákazník.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.34,0:06:42.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Urobím vám extra špeciál.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.78,0:06:44.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,J-Jasné...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.24,0:06:47.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Je pravda, že to bola šarmantná osoba...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.01,0:06:51.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale to je všetko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.12,0:06:53.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hm, dosť podozrivé...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.32,0:06:56.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hej, rozhodne podozrivé.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.66,0:06:59.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jeden z Drakov nebies, Seiichiro Aoki?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.86,0:07:00.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Áno?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.99,0:07:03.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Zdá sa, že je to dobrý rodinný človek.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.80,0:07:06.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aj keď pred pár minútami sa stal opäť slobodným.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.93,0:07:11.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inými slovami, prijal si jeho výzvu?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.24,0:07:13.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Zdá sa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.74,0:07:15.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,V každom prípade
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.24,0:07:18.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,si nemyslím, že Drak nebies príde sám.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.74,0:07:20.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pošlem ti posilu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.75,0:07:23.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nie, mnou sa netráp.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.28,0:07:25.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Som si istý, že príde sám.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.55,0:07:27.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Určite.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.52,0:07:29.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nuž, neskôr sa s tebou spojím.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.32,0:07:34.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Niečo som zistila.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.16,0:07:35.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,O tom, kto si.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prezident Farmaceutík Tojo
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.40,0:07:44.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,mal vnučku menom Kazuki, ktorá zomrela na chorobu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.80,0:07:48.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Čoskoro na to jej otec spáchal samovraždu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.74,0:07:52.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Farmaceutiká Tojo vtedy začali s výskumom klonov.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.05,0:07:55.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inými slovami, prezident Tojo
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.85,0:08:00.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,sa ju pokúsil znovu vytvoriť pomocou Kazukinej maternice a jej otca.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.92,0:08:04.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Toto povedal Beast.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.89,0:08:08.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ja som Kazuki?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.16,0:08:11.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Si Kazuki a si aj jej otec.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prečo robiť niečo také?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.03,0:08:14.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Z akého dôvodu?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.30,0:08:17.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nuž, to neviem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.24,0:08:18.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pozrime sa...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.34,0:08:22.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Je ťažké pochopiť, čo ľudia robia.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.51,0:08:25.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ani Beast na to určite nebude vedieť odpovedať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.58,0:08:27.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale najskôr, Nataku...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.31,0:08:30.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chcem ťa požiadať o láskavosť. Smiem?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.05,0:08:36.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Um, tu je Aoki...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.26,0:08:40.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, prepáčte, že som vám volala do práce.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.33,0:08:41.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nie, to je v poriadku.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.89,0:08:43.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stalo sa niečo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.53,0:08:47.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hej, chcem sa o niečom porozprávať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.40,0:08:48.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ak to nebude vadiť,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.70,0:08:51.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,môžete prísť po práci ku mne?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.94,0:08:53.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,K vám domov?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.51,0:08:56.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Určite vám touto náhlou žiadosťou robím problémy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.84,0:09:00.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nie, to zvládnem, ak to bude okolo deviatej...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.18,0:09:01.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Som rada.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.61,0:09:03.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Budem čakať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.72,0:09:04.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.60,0:09:20.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prečo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.83,0:09:23.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prečo sa diabol ako ty zrodil zo mňa?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.57,0:09:25.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Už to znova neurobím, mami!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.10,0:09:28.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Keby si tu nebola, nemusela by som sa takto skrývať!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.34,0:09:29.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prepáč! Prepáč!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.04,0:09:31.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Už ma nebudeš viac klamať, diabol.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.98,0:09:34.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nikto nebude smutný, keď tu nebudeš!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.01,0:09:36.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Aj keby som zomrela?\N- Správne!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.02,0:09:38.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nikto by neplakal!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.48,0:09:39.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prečo by sa obťažovali?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.19,0:09:45.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mami, čo sa deje?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.42,0:09:46.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mami!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.49,0:09:47.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mami!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.76,0:09:49.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mami, čo sa deje?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.70,0:09:50.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mami!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mami!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.56,0:09:55.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mami!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.11,0:10:10.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prepáčte, že som vás takto zavolala.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.35,0:10:11.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To je v poriadku.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.88,0:10:14.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Môžete sa posadiť?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.09,0:10:15.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jasné.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.46,0:10:22.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Zdá sa, že o tohto kamaráta sa dobre staráte.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.50,0:10:26.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, to je pravda.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.73,0:10:28.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Je to jediná rodina, ktorú mám.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.17,0:10:31.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nech sa páči.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.30,0:10:32.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ďakujem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.47,0:10:35.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Počula som o Saikim...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.38,0:10:38.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To bolo veľmi smutné...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.54,0:10:43.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Vraj to bol váš synovec.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.68,0:10:45.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Určite vás to veľmi tvrdo zasiahlo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.05,0:10:47.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Súcitím s vami.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.02,0:10:52.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Daisuke ma prinútil sľúbiť mu,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.53,0:10:55.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,že nebudem plakať, ak zomrie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.90,0:11:01.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rozhodol sa chrániť princeznú Hinoto, už keď bol veľmi mladý.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.73,0:11:04.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Povedal mi, že nemám plakať, keď zomrie,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.74,0:11:09.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,pretože to sa stane vtedy, keď ju bude chrániť až do samého konca.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.17,0:11:11.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kedy ste mu to sľúbili?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.51,0:11:13.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Keď mal trinásť rokov.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.18,0:11:19.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Je ťažké neplakať, keď zomrie niekto milovaný.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.62,0:11:22.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Takýto sľub nesmiete nikomu nanútiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.16,0:11:28.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mimochodom, žena a dcéra sa majú dobre?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.49,0:11:32.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Áno, ale vzhľadom na boj, ktorý ma čaká,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.40,0:11:34.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,musím sa pripraviť na najhoršie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.73,0:11:36.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Preto ste podali žiadosť o rozvod?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.77,0:11:39.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prepáčte.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.07,0:11:41.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Práve som tam bola.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.81,0:11:44.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Podávala som žiadosť o zmenu adresy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.38,0:11:46.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ch-Chápem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.95,0:11:49.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mohli ste ma pozdraviť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.58,0:11:53.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chcela som, ale vyzerali ste veľmi vážne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.75,0:11:56.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prepáčte.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.25,0:11:58.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rozhodol som sa pre rozvod,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.92,0:12:02.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,aby som do toho všetkého nezatiahol moju rodinu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.59,0:12:05.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale keď skončí finálny boj,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.03,0:12:08.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,a ak to prežijem,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.63,0:12:11.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,určite si znovu zoberiem svoju ženu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.70,0:12:12.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chápem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.94,0:12:14.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To je úľava.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.87,0:12:16.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Som rada.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.61,0:12:19.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Takže o tomto ste chceli hovoriť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.71,0:12:22.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prepáčte, že som vám narobil starosti.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.48,0:12:25.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Musím sa čoskoro vrátiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.35,0:12:27.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prosím, ospravedlňte ma.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.09,0:12:30.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Počkajte.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.72,0:12:31.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nemôžete sa vrátiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.00,0:12:39.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ja pôjdem na Tokijskú stanicu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.70,0:12:43.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nie, sľúbil som, že pôjdem sám.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.14,0:12:44.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.20,0:12:46.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Vy máte rodinu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.34,0:12:50.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Veľa ľudí by za vami smútilo, keby sa vám niečo stalo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.38,0:12:51.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aj za vami...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.81,0:12:53.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ja nemám nikoho.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.91,0:12:56.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pre mňa nebude nikto plakať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.35,0:12:57.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To nie je možné...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.68,0:13:01.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dôvod, prečo som chcela, aby ste prišli, je, aby som vám to povedala.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.79,0:13:03.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Na vás niekto čaká.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.92,0:13:07.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui a ostatní sú ešte mladí a majú budúcnosť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.13,0:13:09.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Takže by som mala byť prvá, kto bude čeliť nebezpečenstvu,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.80,0:13:13.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,pretože nikto nebude smutný, keď sa mi niečo stane.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.00,0:13:17.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Myslíte, že budem s niečím takým súhlasiť?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.50,0:13:22.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Preto som sa pohrala s vaším čajom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.41,0:13:23.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Karen...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.52,0:13:36.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Poe, stráž pána Aokiho.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.76,0:13:39.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Keď sa zobudí, bude po všetkom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.34,0:13:52.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.07,0:13:57.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ostáva ešte pätnásť minút.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.08,0:13:58.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Unáhlený človek.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.57,0:14:28.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Si sám?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.57,0:14:32.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Očakávala som toho, čo robí na úrade.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.71,0:14:36.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ani ty nie si tá, na koho som čakal.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.15,0:14:39.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inými slovami sme obaja zabrali niekoho miesto.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.22,0:14:42.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Avšak zničenie bariér
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.09,0:14:44.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,je želanie Kamuiho Drakov zeme.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.66,0:14:46.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ja sa ním budem riadiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.63,0:14:47.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chápem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.26,0:14:54.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Unáhlení ľudia nie sú veľmi obľúbení!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.04,0:15:06.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Budeš pokračovať?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.75,0:15:08.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Určite nemáš rád smrť, však?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.05,0:15:11.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prestaň sa snažiť zničiť bariéry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.78,0:15:15.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prečo nemám mať rád umieranie?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.62,0:15:19.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nemám také city.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.37,0:15:33.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tvoje oči...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.97,0:15:35.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ako stratené dieťa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.88,0:15:39.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stratené dieťa?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.11,0:15:41.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Správne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pretože som bola rovnaká.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.18,0:15:46.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tie veci povedali, že on je ten,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.59,0:15:50.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,kto držal sedem hviezd vo svojej pravej ruke.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.19,0:15:55.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Poznám tie skutky a tú prácu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.06,0:15:58.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.73,0:16:00.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Modli sa za tvoju matku.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Poď sem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.24,0:16:08.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.12,0:16:19.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Som diabol!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.05,0:16:21.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Môžete sa ma zbaviť?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.99,0:16:23.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Skúste to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.96,0:16:26.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aj keď možno zhoríte.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.36,0:16:27.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ste prekvapený?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.63,0:16:29.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Á-Áno...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.43,0:16:32.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Takže sa predsa bojíte diabla?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.40,0:16:34.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Samozrejme.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.27,0:16:36.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Každý sa bojí.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.50,0:16:37.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Avšak diabol
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.70,0:16:42.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,nemá oči plné strachu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.14,0:16:45.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Moja mama povedala, že som diabol.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.34,0:16:48.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Povedala, že táto sila je sila diabla!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.81,0:16:51.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To si nemyslím.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.35,0:16:56.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sila je niečo, čo sa dá využiť na dobro aj zlo
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.55,0:16:59.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,podľa toho, ako ju použiješ.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.43,0:17:03.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nepoznám význam tej sily.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.40,0:17:07.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale verím, že je to niečo, čo ti dal náš Pán,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.30,0:17:09.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,keď si sa narodila do tohto sveta.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.97,0:17:13.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Som si istý, že ťa časom zavedie k odpovedi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.31,0:17:14.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Klamete!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.34,0:17:16.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Som diabol!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.98,0:17:21.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pre mňa si len zatúlaná malá ovečka...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.06,0:17:39.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ver si.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.20,0:17:44.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A trpezlivo čakaj, než ti Pán ukáže odpoveď.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.98,0:17:57.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A teraz sa spolu pomodlime.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.02,0:18:04.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Je ťažké nevedieť, čo vlastne naozaj si...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.19,0:18:11.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nie je nič také, ako tvor bez emócií.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.10,0:18:13.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Určite máš aj ty emócie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.88,0:18:27.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pánovi Aokimu sa nepodarilo prísť?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.48,0:18:29.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mám s ním dohodnuté stretnutie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.85,0:18:34.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hej, náhle sa mu zmenili plány, takže som prišla namiesto neho.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.22,0:18:35.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sklamaný?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.39,0:18:36.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.96,0:18:38.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Používate vodu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.82,0:18:40.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Môj make-up bude zničený.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.03,0:18:44.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Som si istý, že ste krajšia bez make-upu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.80,0:18:46.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Vďaka.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.63,0:18:50.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Už som unavený, pretože som dlho nepoužíval vodné triky.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.74,0:18:52.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Asi starnem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.57,0:18:55.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, ešte musíte byť mladý.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.31,0:18:56.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Len sa tak snažím vyzerať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.64,0:19:00.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Toto je pekné.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.11,0:19:02.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, nie, to nič nie je.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.79,0:19:13.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Vážne ste oveľa mladší než ja.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.23,0:19:17.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stratil som rýchlosť, keď som bol zablokovaný ohňom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.33,0:19:21.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ak uhnete, nič dobré z toho pre mňa nevzíde.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.23,0:19:23.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To bola náhoda.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.64,0:19:24.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ste skromná.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.08,0:19:36.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale tomuto sa nevyhnete.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.98,0:19:39.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aká krása...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.05,0:19:42.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ako kvet, ktorý kvitne pod vodou.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.63,0:19:54.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pán Aoki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.57,0:20:01.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prišli ste, ako ste sľúbili.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.41,0:20:03.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Vedel som to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.58,0:20:07.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale nezdá sa, že ste v najlepšej forme.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.18,0:20:11.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aj môj kamarát je zranený.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.85,0:20:15.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Keďže sa obaja musíme postarať o našich partnerov,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.25,0:20:17.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,čo keby sme to dnes ukončili remízou?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.46,0:20:19.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.52,0:20:21.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale keď bude toto pokračovať,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.06,0:20:24.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,chcem byť vaším súperom ja.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.43,0:20:26.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Budem si to pamätať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.70,0:20:27.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Majte sa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.27,0:20:34.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tá rana...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.04,0:20:39.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Urobili ste si to sám, aby ste nezaspali.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.14,0:20:44.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Požičal som si nožík na ovocie...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.12,0:20:45.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prečo ste urobili niečo také?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.05,0:20:48.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Vaša žena bude mať o vás starosť!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.05,0:20:52.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Presne to chcem povedať ja.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.96,0:20:56.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ak zomriete, nikto nebude plakať...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.83,0:20:59.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To ste mysleli vážne?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.33,0:21:03.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nezvyknem sa nahnevať,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.94,0:21:07.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,ale ak ešte raz urobíte niečo také...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.14,0:21:09.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A znova pôjdete sama...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.34,0:21:11.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Veľmi sa nahnevám.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.88,0:21:18.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rozumiete, Karen?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.15,0:21:19.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pán Aoki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.58,0:21:24.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Trochu si tu zdriemnem...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.13,0:21:36.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A teraz sa spolu pomodlime.
